*Kapetane* su često vezani za nekakve avanture i avanturističke price. (Captains are often associated with some adventures and adventurous stories.)

Mnogi *kapetane* su poznati po svojim hrabrim i odvažnim postupcima. (Many captains are known for their brave and courageous deeds.)

*Kapetan* je morao biti snalažljiv da bi izbegao nevolje. (The captain had to be resourceful in order to avoid trouble.)

*Kapetanu* je bilo potrebno mnogo veštine da bi se kretao kroz neprijateljske vode. (The captain needed a lot of skill to maneuver through hostile waters.)

*Kapetanima* je često bilo potrebno da preuzmu velike odgovornosti u vreme najtežih trenutaka. (Captains often had to take on great responsibilities in times of greatest distress.)